搞亂，做on9嘢俾子彈對手，都唔割？？？<br />\n<br />\n勇武撚請諗一諗<br />\n勇武，都要醒目地勇武"},{"pid":"282d978310c49c66111f0bc69fc88c9cfe9bcc2f","tid":1469711,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:28:52.000Z","msg":"經過812同813我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468682</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee84be2e66e26379a7ac5ff5f419d154b7eea374","tid":1469711,"uid":276826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44cfb98b78912be3f459e9ab092e3d3106c9763a","tid":1469711,"uid":252486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bef94f14815b069eaf5ded09865598e06d4dee8","tid":1469711,"uid":170014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f522dbe0f8d78010c7ecf620ec5a1f455e6a4f76","tid":1469711,"uid":252486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:48:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌米L中計呀！！！！！！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係專登放條友出黎等你哋捉，等其他人，媒體！覺得我哋係暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n人地港澳通行證下面個行係： <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">派發機關</span></strong><br />\n<strong>公安部出入境管理局</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">派發機關呀</span></span><br />\n姐係好似我哋passport咁咋<br />\n<br />\n屌米L中計呀！！！！！！！！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">負評 上一頁</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:50:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係米而家事實係到！唔撚想相信就要屌？！</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"你真係唔係鬼就一定係on9 <br />\n尋晚有post fced<br />\n負評 上一頁"}]}